data.name: Particle Accumulator - Energy I
data.propertySkillDes: A low-spec particle accumulator, suited for units that favor energy attacks. Deals additional damage equal to 10% of the target's max HP.

data.name: Particle Accumulator - Energy II
data.propertySkillDes: A particle accumulator which can achieve greater particle intensity, suited for units that favor energy attacks. Deals additional damage equal to 20% of the target's max HP.

data.name: Particle Accumulator - Dynamic I
data.propertySkillDes: A low-spec particle accumulator. Equipping it greatly increases the firepower of a weapon. Damage dealt increases by 5% when equipped.

data.name: Particle Accumulator - Dynamic II
data.propertySkillDes: A particle accumulator which can achieve greater particle intensity, suited for units that favor energy attacks. Damage dealt increases by 10% when equipped.

data.name: Particle Accumulator - Ion I
data.propertySkillDes: A low-spec particle accumulator, suited for units that favor ion attacks. Grants 15 points of ion reduction

data.name: Particle Accumulator - Ion II
data.propertySkillDes: A particle accumulator which can achieve greater particle intensity, suited for units that favor ion attacks. Grants 30 points of ion reduction

data.name: Particle Accumulator - Stability I
data.propertySkillDes:
A low-spec particle accumulator. Equipping it allows you to more easily break enemy units' stability.
Once configured, it increases the unit’s stability index reduction by 15%.

data.name: Particle Accumulator - Stability II
data.propertySkillDes:
A particle accumulator which can achieve greater particle intensity. Equipping it allows you to more easily break enemy units' stability.
Once configured, it increases the unit’s stability index reduction by 30%.
